<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.6.7">
<l>aṇaṅkuk karumarunteṉ ṟaṅkōrāṭuṅ kaḷḷum parāyc</l>
<l>cuṇaṅkai yeṟintu nuntōḷ kulaikkappaṭu maṉṉaimī</l>
<l>ruṇaṅkal keṭakkaḻutai yutaṭāṭ ṭaṅkaṇ ṭeṉpayaṉ</l>
<l>vaṇaṅkīr kaṇmāyap pirāṉṟamar vētamval lāraiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As a precious remedy for [this] girl a goat and toddy are spread there,</l>
<l>the Cuṇaṅkai is beaten [and] your shoulders are shaken, mothers.</l>
<l>Seeing the dance of a donkey’s lip as the corn is lost, what is the use?</l>
<l>Bow before the people of the marvellous lord that master the Veda.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
